results.deck: ImaginEngine is a Foundation 9 Entertainment studio.
results.description:
ImaginEngine is part of the game-developer company Foundation 9 Entertainment, and is mostly developing children's video games and software. 
 
In 2003 ImaginEngine and Digital Eclipse Software merged to form Backbone Entertainment. 
In 2005 Backbone Entertainment merged with The Collective, Inc. and Pipeworks Software to form Foundation 9 Entertainment.
